                    <h3>Neurostream v0.0.2 — Visualization Improvements & Bug Fixes</h3>
                    <p>This patch release improves EEG trace rendering quality and resolves minor UI issues discovered after the initial release.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Improved OpenGL visualizer with anti-aliased line rendering (4× MSAA, line smoothing, alpha blending) for smoother EEG traces</li>
                        <li>Implemented DPI-aware amplitude scaling to ensure consistent µV/mm representation across different displays</li>
                        <li>Fixed annotation banner visibility issue in the UI</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>This release focuses on visual accuracy and rendering quality improvements for the EEG display engine.</p>
